name: Cosmo Queen - Mistress Of The Stars
effect:
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must first be Special Summoned by banishing 1 "Cosmo Queen" from your hand or Deck. When this card leaves the field, target 1 banished "Cosmo Queen"; Special Summon it, and if you do, it cannot be targeted or destroyed by card effects, until the end of this turn.
Once per turn, you can activate 1 of these effects:
● Target 1 "Cosmo-Spacian" monster in your GY; equipt that target to this card.
● Target 1 face-up card your opponent controls, banish this card, and if you do, send 1 "Cosmo-Spacian" monster from your Deck to your GY.
